rick deckard is a fictional character and the protagonist of philip k. dick 's 1968 novel do androids dream of electric sheep?.   he was portrayed by harrison ford in the 1982 film adaptation blade runner directed by ridley scott and by james purefoy in the 2014 bbc radio 4 adaptation directed by sasha yevtushenko.http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b047cz98    overview   rick deckard ( a play on the name rene descartes )   is a specialist plainclothes police officer with the san francisco police department in the early 21st century , who goes after " andys " as they are called .

